{"tid":2517081,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中方要求取消頒麥凱恩公共服務領袖獎予蔡英文","createTime":"2021-05-05T05:48:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T06:22:48.000Z","uid":66324,"like":4,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"9f4e2083868716416b1bb8b5a7b6e1011706a5a9","tid":2517081,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:48:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/734125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F734125&d=d89kjzbMxLru5B8Znw6mnw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=e26b5b72\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fnews%2Farticle%2F37%2F734125&h=1a96d554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/news/article/37/734125</a>"},{"pid":"9fcfcd4b8c6085cfaa1ba688854ef2dc2f3f187d","tid":2517081,"uid":66324,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:49:02.000Z","msg":"【有線新聞】中國駐加拿大使館，不滿哈里法斯國際安全論壇頒發「麥凱恩公共服務領袖獎」予台灣的蔡英文總統，要求取消頒獎的「錯誤決定」。<br />\n大使館發言人指，論壇不顧中方嚴正立場，執意向蔡英文頒獎，嚴重違反一個中國原則，向台獨分裂勢力發出錯誤信號，中方堅決反對，敦促論壇充分認清台灣議題的高度敏感性。<br />\n論壇將今年的領袖獎頒予蔡英文，讚揚她堅持並勇於抗衡北京施壓、捍衛自由價值，說會邀請蔡英文今年稍後親身到加拿大領獎。"},{"pid":"f05d9b2c81b60ef84a772f4dd8a88e83c176302f","tid":2517081,"uid":182475,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"叫翠翠直接搵麥凱恩講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a197ec043618ae7de7aa2b1ba2eaffe477ab5e","tid":2517081,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:52:38.000Z","msg":"翠翠冇獎拎呷醋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e09e67c007931adebded16d37a9bfbfd8ce591d","tid":2517081,"uid":260271,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T05:54:27.000Z","msg":"你支那做ge野就係人地頒獎ge原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"803afdc8939d9085d52466abfa7daf6f46de